 *
 * This function cannot be called in a scan callback
 * because of deadlock.
 *
 * @param callback
 *   The function to be called which can update the devargs list.
 * @param user_arg
 *   An opaque pointer passed to callback.
 * @return
 *   0 on success, negative on error
 */</doc>
